# Images are intentionally NOT tracked. The analyst-grounding skill only reads
# text (it ignores images), so keeping them out makes this repo lightweight and
# fast to clone. Originals are always reachable via each article's 原文链接.
# To make this a full mirror instead, delete the two lines below.
output_by_account/**/images/
**/images/

# secrets / local scraper state
.auth
*.log
__pycache__/
.venv/
.DS_Store
